%20about%20betraying%20youth%20and%20stall%20employment.%20Now%20they%20are%20getting%20exposed%20as%20people%20are%20rejecting%20their%20lies%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20skill%20development%20and%20employment%20are%20needed%20in%20the%20country%20and%20his%20government%20is%20working%20in%20this%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Maharashtra%20has%20a%20glorious%20history%2C%20a%20capable%20present%20and%20the%20dream%20of%20a%20prosperous%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20state%20that%20has%20a%20critical%20role%20to%20play%20in%20Viksit%20Bharat%20as%20it%20has%20power%20of%20industry%2C%20agriculture%20and%20finance%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20aim%20is%20to%20make%20Maharashtra%20the%20world's%20big%20financial%20powerhouse%20and%20to%20make%20Mumbai%20a%20global%20fintech%20capital%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20aim%20is%20to%20improve%20everyone's%20standard%20of%20living%20and%20make%20quality%20of%20life%20the%20best.%20This%20is%20why%20efforts%20are%20being%20made%20to%20better%20the%20connectivity%20of%20areas%20close%20to%20Mumbai%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PM%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ground%20breaking%20of%20infrastructure%20works%20come%20months%20ahead%20of%20the%20state%20assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20upcoming%20infrastructure%20projects%20in%20and%20around%20Mumbai%20will%20boost%20connectivity%20of%20the%20city%20with%20nearby%20areas%2C%20which%20ensures%20better%20facilities%20as%20well%20as%20safety%20for%20women%2C%20PM%20Modi%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20expansion%20of%20the%20metro%20rail%20network%20in%20the%20metropolis%20was%20going%20on%20at%20a%20rapid%20pace%2C%20rising%20from%20just%208%20kilometres%20ten%20years%20ago%20to%2080%20kilometres%20now%2C%20while%20work%20on%20200%20kilometres%20is%20underway%2C%20the%20PM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20length%20of%20national%20highways%20has%20trebled%2C%20adding%20the%20Goregaon-Mulund%20Link%20Road%2C%20which%20will%20act%20as%20a%20major%20east-west%20connector%20in%20the%20northern%20part%20of%20the%20city%2C%20was%20a%20fine%20example%20of%20balance%20between%20conserving%20nature%20and%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20twin%20tunnels%20connecting%20Thane%20and%20Borivali%20will%20ensure%20the%20distance%20between%20the%20two%20areas%20will%20be%20covered%20in%20minutes%2C%20the%20PM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Coastal%20Road%20and%20Atal%20Setu%20are%20now%20complete%2C%20the%20PM%20said%2C%20and%20recalled%20efforts%20by%20some%20to%20stall%20the%20sea%20bridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20now%20everyone%20realises%20how%20beneficial%20it%20is%2C%20the%20PM%20said%20about%20the%20Atal%20Setu%2C%20the%20country's%20longest%20sea%20bridge%20connecting%20Mumbai%20and%20Navi%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%2020%2C000%20vehicles%20use%20it%20everyday%20and%20it%20is%20estimated%20that%20Rs%2020-25%20lakh%20worth%20of%20fuel%20is%20saved%20and%20people%20take%20less%20time%20to%20reach%20Panvel%2C%20the%20PM%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20transformation%20of%20railways%20is%20benefitting%20Mumbai%20and%20Maharashtra%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20redevelopment%20works%20of%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20Terminus%20and%20Ajni-Nagpur%20were%20happening%20at%20a%20rapid%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20platforms%20at%20CSMT%20and%20Lokmanya%20Tilak%20Terminus%20(two%20of%20the%20main%20junctions%20of%20Central%20Railway%20in%20Mumbai)%2C%20have%20been%20inaugurated%20and%20will%20enable%20the%20railways%20to%20run%2024-coach%20trains%2C%20the%20PM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20has%20also%20approved%20the%20Rs%2076000%20crore%20Vadhavan%20port%20in%20Dahanu%20in%20Palghar%2C%20which%20will%20generate%2010%20lakh%20jobs%2C%20the%20PM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20