om.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Falec-baldwin-halyna-hutchins-gloria-allred-lawsuit-1236071092%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Falec-baldwin-halyna-hutchins-gloria-allred-lawsuit-1236071092%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCurrent%20World%20Order%20Is%20WWII%20Winners'%20Club%2C%20Needs%20Reform%26quot%3B%3A%20Lankan%20Minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESri%20Lanka%20wants%20to%20capitalise%20on%20India's%20growth%20and%20it%20has%20given%20an%20assurance%20that%20it%20will%20not%20allow%20any%20country%2C%20including%20China%2C%20to%20use%20it%20in%20a%20way%20that%20harms%20New%20Delhi's%20security%20concerns%2C%20the%20island%20nation's%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Foreign%20Affairs%2C%20Tharaka%20Balasuriya%2C%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20wide-ranging%20conversation%20on%20NDTV%20Dialogues%2C%20Mr%20Balasuriya%20stressed%20on%20the%20alignment%20between%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20India%20in%20terms%20of%20increasing%20connectivity%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20and%20also%20said%20that%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20changing%20the%20current%20financial%20and%20political%20architecture%20of%20the%20world%2C%20which%20he%20called%20a%20%26quot%3BSecond%20World%20War%20winners'%20club%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20India's%20concerns%20about%20China%2C%20including%20the%20docking%20of%20Chinese%20spy%20ships%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20the%20minister%2C%20who%20was%20in%20New%20Delhi%20for%20the%20BIMSTEC%20Foreign%20Ministers'%20Retreat%2C%20insisted%20that%20the%20vessels%20were%20at%20the%20ports%20only%20for%20replenishment%20and%20not%20for%20any%20kind%20of%20surveys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20sure%20India%20will%20have%20security%20concerns.%20It's%20natural%20when%20you%20are%20becoming%20a%20bigger%20and%20bigger%20power%2C%20a%20more%20important%20player%20in%20world%20politics%2C%20to%20have%20concerns.%20But%2C%20from%20Sri%20Lanka's%20perspective%2C%20we%20have%20given%20an%20assurance%20that%20we%20will%20ensure%20that%20no%20country%20uses%20Sri%20Lanka%20in%20any%20way%20to%20harm%20India's%20security%20concerns.%20Of%20course%2C%20that%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20we%20don't%20want%20to%20trade%20with%20China...%20I%20think%20we%20need%20to%20have%20a%20distinction%20between%20what's%20harmful%20for%20India's%20security%20concerns%2C%20and%20trade%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Indian%20Foreign%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar's%20warning%20of%20a%20debt%20trap%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20which%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20reference%20to%20China%2C%20Mr%20Balasuriya%20was%20candid%20and%20said%20that%20when%20Sri%20Lanka's%20economic%20crisis%20began%2C%20only%2010%25%20of%20its%20foreign%20debt%20was%20to%20Beijing.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20have%20had%20a%20debt%20issue%2C%20then%20there's%20no%20point%20in%20us%20blaming%20this%20or%20that%20country.%20The%20reason%20we%20got%20into%20this%20situation%20is%20our%20own%20doing%20and%20we%20can't%20blame%20other%20countries%20for%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20admitted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWorld%20Order%20Reforms%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20calls%20from%20India%20and%20other%20countries%20for%20reform%20of%20multilateral%20institutions%20like%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council%2C%20the%20World%20Bank%20and%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%2C%20especially%20in%20view%20of%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20and%20Israel-Hamas%20conflicts%2C%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20minister%20said%20something%20like%20that%20is%20much%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20the%20current%20world%20order%2C%20it's%20a%20Second%20World%20War%20winners'%20club.%20In%201945%2C%20the%20UK%20controlled%20about%2010%25%20of%20the%20world's%20GDP%2C%20largely%20thanks%20to%20India%2C%20and%20also%20a%20large%20population.%20But%20now%20they%20are%20not%20as%20significant.%20But%20it's%20not%20just%20a%20question%20of%20India...%20African%20and%20Latin%20American%20countries%20also%20don't%20have%20a%20veto%20or%20a%20voice%20in%20the%20Security%20Council%20in%20terms%20of%20permanent%20membership.%20So%2C%20certainly%2C%20both%20the%20political%20and%20financial%20architectures%20have%20to%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Balasuriya%20emphasised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20think%20India%20certainly%20has%20a%20very%20large%20role%20to%20play.%20It%20has%20been%20a%20leader%20in%20the%20Global%20South.%20But%2C%20sometimes%2C%20India%20also%20needs%20to%20compromise%20its%20interest%20against%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20and%20take%20a%20leadership%20position%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20that%20India%20should%20have%20a%20position%20in%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20and%20called%20for%20African%20and%20Latin%20American%20countries%20to%20have%20one%20too.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20look%20at%20the%20overall%20structure%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia-Sri%20Lanka%20Ties%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Balasuriya%20said%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20Initiative%20for%20Multi-Sectoral%20Technical%20and%20Economic%20Cooperation%20(BIMSTEC)%20Foreign%20Ministers'%20Retreat%20was%20held%20in%20an%20informal%20atmosphere%20and%20there%20was%20a%20free%20flow%20of%20ideas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20particularly%20liked%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20point%20that%20while%20the%20European%20Union%20had%20been%20very%20successful%2C%20South%20Asia%20had%20fallen%20short%2C%20primarily%20because%20of%20connectivity%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmphasising%20that%20Sri%20Lanka's%20people-to-people%20connectivity%20with%20India%20has%20always%20been%20strong%2C%20he%20said%20his%20country%20is%20looking%20to%20take%20that%20even%20further.%20Sea%2C%20air%2C%20and%20grid%20connectivity%20with%20India%20are%20also%20priorities%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20Mr%20Jaishankar's%20first%20visit%20in%20PM%20Modi's%20third%20term%20being%20to%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20a%20proposed%20bridge%20between%20the%20two%20countries%2C%20Mr%20Balasuriya%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFrom%20Sri%20Lanka's%20perspective%20greater%20connectivity%20will%20be%20a%20game-changer.%20Apart%20from%20Gujarat%2C%20four%20of%20the%20fastest-growing%20states%20in%20India%20are%20in%20the%20south.%20For%20example%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20140%20million%20internal%20tourists%20and%20Rameshwaram%2C%20which%20is%20the%20closest%20point%20to%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20has%2010%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20we%20want%20to%20start%20the%20ferry%20service%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%20and%20maybe%20tourists%20can%20come%20visit%20the%20Shiva%20Temple%20in%20Sri%20Lanka's%20Mannar.%20So%20we%20are%20very%20interested%20in%20capitalising%20on%20India's%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFishermen%20Arrests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arrest%20of%20Indian%20fishermen%20has%20been%20a%20long-standing%20issue%20between%20Colombo%20and%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Mr%20Balasuriya%20acknowledged%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20in%20the%20foreign%20ministry%20reading%20old%20notes%20and%20found%20correspondence%20between%20Prime%20Minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Sirimavo%20Bandaranaike%20in%20the%201950s%2C%20and%20the%20fishermen%20issue%20was%20on%20top%20of%20the%20agenda%20even%20then.%20But%20the%20problem%20is%20that%20it's%20not%20just%20one%20or%20two%20Indian%20fishermen%2C%20thousands%20come%20to%20Sri%20Lankan%20waters...%20And%20people%20in%20north%20Sri%20Lanka%20are%20deprived%20of%20their%20livelihood%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20growing%20connectivity%20between%20India%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20can%20be%20a%20ray%20of%20hope%20in%20this%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20who%20are%20into%20fishing%20(in%20Sri%20Lanka)%20could%20move%20to%20the%20tourism%20industry%20if%20they%20can%20make%20more%20money%20there.%20India%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20have%20to%20look%20at%20fishing%20from%20a%20sustainability%20perspective%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720893120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fh7bb5h9o_tharaka-balasuriya_625x300_13_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcurrent-world-order-is-wwii-winners-club-needs-reform-lankan-minister-6099782%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sri%20Lanka%20wants%20to%20capitalise%20on%20India's%20growth%20and%20it%20has%20given%20an%20assurance%20that%20it%20will%20not%20allow%20any%20country%2C%20including%20China%2C%20to%20use%20it%20in%20a%20way%20that%20harms%20New%20Delhi's%20security%20concerns%2C%20the%20island%20nation's%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Foreign%20Affairs%2C%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcurrent-world-order-is-wwii-winners-club-needs-reform-lankan-minister-6099782%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcurrent-world-order-is-wwii-winners-club-needs-reform-lankan-minister-6099782%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcurrent-world-order-is-wwii-winners-club-needs-reform-lankan-minister-6099782%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22OpenAI%20Whistleblowers%20Seek%20Probe%20Into%20%26quot%3BRestrictive%20Non-Disclosures%26quot%3B%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20whistleblowers%20have%20filed%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20U.S.%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%2C%20calling%20for%20an%20investigation%20over%20the%20artificial%20intelligence%20company's%20allegedly%20restrictive%20non-disclosure%20agreements%2C%20the%20Washington%20Post%20reported%20on%20Saturday%2C%20citing%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20letter%20sent%20to%20the%20SEC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20whistleblowers%20alleged%20that%20OpenAI%20issued%20overly%20restrictive%20employment%2C%20severance%2C%20and%20nondisclosure%20agreements%20to%20its%20employees%2C%20which%20could%20have%20led%20to%20penalties%20against%20workers%20who%20raised%20concerns%20about%20OpenAI%20to%20federal%20authorities%2C%20according%20to%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20company%20made%20employees%20sign%20agreements%20that%20required%20them%20to%20waive%20their%20federal%20rights%20to%20whistleblower%20compensation%2C%20according%20to%20the%20letter%20seen%20by%20the%20Washington%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agreements%20also%20required%20that%20employees%20get%20prior%20consent%20from%20the%20company%20if%20they%20wanted%20to%20disclose%20information%20to%20federal%20regulators%2C%20the%20newspaper%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20OpenAI%20did%20not%20create%20exemptions%20in%20the%20employee%20nondisparagement%20clauses%20for%20disclosing%20securities%20violations%20to%20the%20SEC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20SEC%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20an%20emailed%20statement%20that%20it%20does%20not%20comment%20on%20the%20existence%20or%20nonexistence%20of%20a%20possible%20whistleblower%20submission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20a%20comment%20on%20the%20Washington%20Post%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpenAI's%20chatbots%20with%20generative%20AI%20capabilities%2C%20such%20as%20engaging%20in%20human-like%20conversations%20and%20creating%20images%20based%20on%20text%20prompts%2C%20have%20stirred%20safety%20concerns%20as%20AI%20models%20become%20powerful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20in%20May%20formed%20a%20Safety%20and%20Security%20Committee%20that%20will%20be%20led%20by%20board%20members%2C%20including%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20as%20it%20begins%20training%20its%20next%20artificial%20inte