-under-delhi-s-vehicle-aggregator-scheme-124071300891_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThe%20response%20to%20the%20scheme%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20confidence%20that%20businesses%20have%20in%20our%20vision%20for%20sustainable%20and%20efficient%20urban%20mobility%2C%26quot%3B%20Delhi's%20Transport%20Minister%20Kailash%20Gahlot%20said%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fola-uber-among-21-cos-registered-under-delhi-s-vehicle-aggregator-scheme-124071300891_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fola-uber-among-21-cos-registered-under-delhi-s-vehicle-aggregator-scheme-124071300891_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fola-uber-among-21-cos-registered-under-delhi-s-vehicle-aggregator-scheme-124071300891_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Is%20Biden%20Competent%20For%202nd%20Term%3F%20Health%20Experts%20Call%20Out%20%26quot%3BRaging%20Ageism%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20Joe%20Biden's%20verbal%20gaffes%2C%20shaky%20voice%2C%20and%20other%20troubling%20signs%20have%20brought%20an%20intense%20focus%20on%20the%20US%20President's%20mental%20acuity%2C%20health%20experts%20are%20calling%20on%20him%20and%20rival%20Donald%20Trump%20to%20pass%20additional%20cognitive%20tests%2C%20even%20while%20warning%20against%20leaping%20to%20conclusions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20tests%2C%20experts%20said%2C%20could%20either%20help%20repudiate%20speculation%20that%20the%2081-year-old%20president's%20mental%20state%20is%20in%20worrying%20decline%20--%20or%20else%20confirm%20it%20--%20and%20could%20enlighten%20voters%20on%20the%20mental%20abilities%20of%20Trump%2C%20who%20has%20had%20his%20own%20share%20of%20verbal%20lapses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20reliable%20diagnoses%2C%20they%20caution%2C%20cannot%20be%20made%20from%20afar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Biden's%20disastrous%20performance%20in%20his%20debate%20with%20Trump%20two%20weeks%20ago%2C%20the%20Democrat's%20campaign%20has%20faced%20fierce%20opposition.%20A%20growing%20number%20of%20officials%20in%20his%20own%20party%20are%20questioning%20his%20ability%20to%20lead%20the%20country%20for%20four%20more%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20didn't%20help%20when%20at%20a%20summit%20in%20Washington%20earlier%20this%20week%20Biden%20mistakenly%20introduced%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20as%20his%20foe%20Vladimir%20Putin%2C%20before%20quickly%20correcting%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDennis%20Selkoe%2C%20a%20neurologist%20at%20Harvard%20Medical%20School%2C%20said%20the%20fundamental%20issue%20is%20whether%20Biden%20is%20suffering%20from%20%26quot%3Ba%20normal%20age-related%20process%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bsomething%20that%20represents%20a%20neurologic%20disease.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaking%20a%20mistake%20with%20a%20name%20is%20not%20automatically%20a%20sign%20of%20dementia%20or%20of%20Alzheimer's%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Selkoe%2C%20who%20sees%20many%20patients%20with%20neurodegenerative%20problems%2C%20said%20Biden%20does%20seem%20to%20have%20the%20%26quot%3Bappearance%20of%20an%20early%20Parkinson%20patient%26quot%3B%20--%20including%20his%20slow%2C%20stiff%20gait%20and%20his%20low%2C%20sometimes%20barely%20audible%20voice%2C%20which%20could%20be%20a%20condition%20known%20as%20hypophonia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDetailed%20Tests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Biden%20underwent%20a%20complete%20physical%20exam.%20A%20published%20summary%20of%20its%20results%20indicated%20that%20an%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20detailed%20neurologic%20exam%26quot%3B%20had%20ruled%20out%20Parkinson's.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20no%20detail%20was%20provided%20on%20the%20exact%20nature%20of%20the%20tests%20or%20their%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECould%20a%20neurological%20illness%20have%20taken%20root%20over%20just%20the%20past%20five%20months%3F%20If%20the%20exams%20in%20February%20had%20been%20comprehensive%2C%20Selkoe%20said%2C%20there%20should%20have%20been%20early%20signs%20of%20a%20nascent%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20editorial%20in%20March%2C%20the%20scientific%20journal%20Lancet%20called%20for%20standardized%20procedures%20to%20examine%20the%20health%20of%20sitting%20and%20prospective%20presidents%20to%20insulate%20American%20voters%20from%20a%20%26quot%3Bpestilence%20of%20speculation%2C%20misinformation%2C%20and%20slander.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbsent%20such%20reliable%20testing%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20US%20public%20remains%20beholden%20to%20voluntarily%20released%20reports%20from%20politicians'%20personal%20physicians%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20journal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJay%20Olshansky%2C%20an%20expert%20in%20aging%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Illinois%20at%20Chicago%2C%20sounded%20a%20similar%20note%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20think%20the%20time%20has%20arrived%20for%20complete%20transparency.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20urged%20both%20major%20presidential%20candidates%20to%20pass%20a%20cognitive%20test%2C%20something%20former%20president%20Trump%20has%20frequently%20challenged%20Biden%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20such%20exams%2C%20including%20those%20known%20as%20the%20MMSE%20and%20the%20MoCA%2C%20are%20available%20either%20for%20an%20initial%20screening%20or%20as%20part%20of%20a%20more%20comprehensive%20battery%20of%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20has%20said%20that%20he%20effectively%20passes%20a%20cognitive%20test%20every%20day%2C%20simply%20by%20carrying%20out%20his%20presidential%20duties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20it's%20the%20same%2C%26quot%3B%20Selkoe%20said.%20Being%20able%20to%20conduct%20familiar%20tasks%20one%20has%20done%20for%20years%20is%20one%20thing%2C%20he%20said%2C%20while%20being%20able%20to%20repeat%20a%20list%20of%20words%20heard%20five%20minutes%20earlier%2C%20as%20some%20tests%20require%2C%20is%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20news%20conference%20Thursday%2C%20the%20President%20said%20he%20would%20be%20willing%20to%20take%20a%20new%20neurological%20exam%20if%20his%20doctors%20recommended%20it%2C%20but%20that%20%26quot%3Bno%20one%20is%20suggesting%20that%20to%20me%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStereotypes%20On%20Aging%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAging%20changes%20one's%20brain%2C%20said%20Allison%20Sekuler%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Baycrest%20Academy%2C%20a%20hospital%20specializing%20in%20elderly%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGarbage%20is%20basically%20building%20up%20in%20the%20brain%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20AFP%2C%20adding%20that%20parts%20of%20the%20brain%20atrophy%2C%20or%20shrink%2C%20including%20parts%20important%20to%20memory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20early%20phase%20known%20as%20%26quot%3Bmild%20cognitive%20impairment%26quot%3B%20can%20sometimes%20develop%20into%20Alzheimer's%20or%20some%20other%20form%20of%20dementia%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20their%20recent%20debate%2C%20both%20Biden%20and%20Trump%20--%20who%20is%2078%20--%20%26quot%3Bexhibited%20some%20sort%20of%20issues%20in%20terms%20of%20being%20able%20to%20stay%20on%20track%20with%20a%20question%2C%26quot%3B%20Sekuler%20said%2C%20recommending%20that%20both%20men%20undergo%20testing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20she%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe're%20really%20only%20talking%20about%20one%20of%20them%20right%20now%20because%20that%20aligns%20with%20our%20stereotype%20of%20what%20aging%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOlshansky%20also%20denounced%20what%20he%20called%20%26quot%3Braging%26quot%3B%20ageism%2C%20citing%20a%20recent%20magazine%20cover%20that%20used%20a%20walker%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20the%20Biden-Trump%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%20that%20while%20there%20is%20a%20lower%20age%20limit%20for%20would-be%20US%20presidents%20--%20they%20must%20be%20at%20least%2035%20--%20there%20is%20no%20upper%20limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20he%20called%20%26quot%3Bcrystallized%20intelligence%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20the%20ability%20to%20use%20past%20experience%20to%20improve%20one's%20reasoning%20skills%2C%20%26quot%3Bgets%20stronger%20and%20stronger%26quot%3B%20with%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOlshansky%20co-authored%20a%202020%20study%20that%20gave%20Biden%20a%2095%20percent%20chance%20of%20surviving%20a%20first%20term%2C%20based%20on%20average%20life%20expectancy%20for%20someone%20of%20his%20age%2C%20plus%20personal%20risk%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20similar%20calculation%20four%20years%20later%2C%20on%20a%20man%20now%20four%20years%20older%2C%20gave%20Biden%20a%20much%20lower%20probability%20of%20survival%3A%20just%2075%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720892460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fd1docuf_biden-trump-afp-_625x300_28_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fis-joe-biden-competent-for-2nd-term-as-us-presideny-health-experts-call-out-raging-ageism-6099741%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20Biden's%20verbal%20gaffes%2C%20shaky%20voice%2C%20and%20other%20troubling%20signs%20have%20brought%20an%20intense%20focus%20on%20the%20President's%20mental%20acuity%2C%20experts%20are%20calling%20on%20him%20and%20Trump%20to%20pass%20additional%20cognitive%20tests%2C%20while%20warning%20against%20leaping%20to%20conclusions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fis-joe-biden-competent-for-2nd-term-as-us-presideny-health-experts-call-out-raging-ageism-6099741%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-