two%20Delta%20flight%20attendants%20wearing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fisrael-palestine%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPalestinian%3C%2Fa%3E%20flag%20pins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20post%2C%20which%20incorrectly%20equated%20the%20Palestinian%20flag%20to%20the%20militant%20group%20Hamas'%20flag%2C%20read%3A%20%26quot%3BSince%202001%20we%20take%20our%20shoes%20off%20in%20every%20airport%20because%20a%20terrorist%20attack%20in%20US%20soil.%20Now%20imagine%20getting%20into%20a%20%40Delta%20flight%20and%20seeing%20workers%20with%20Hamas%20badges%20in%20the%20air.%20What%20do%20you%20do%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20since-deleted%20reply%20from%20Delta's%20official%20account%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20hear%20you%20as%20I'd%20be%20terrified%20as%20well%2C%20personally.%20Our%20employees%20reflect%20our%20culture%20and%20we%20do%20not%20take%20it%20lightly%20when%20our%20policy%20is%20not%20being%20followed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnation%2F2024%2F07%2F12%2Fdelta-palestine-flag-pin-apology%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Delta%20apologized%20for%20the%20incident%20and%20said%20it%20had%20taken%20action%20against%20the%20employee%20responsible%20for%20the%20airline's%20post%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20comment%20%26quot%3Bwas%20not%20in%20line%20with%20our%20values%20and%20our%20mission.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20employee%20responsible%20for%20the%20comment%20%26quot%3Bhas%20been%20counseled%20and%20no%20longer%20supports%20Delta's%20social%20channels%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20airline%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEdward%20Ahmed%20Mitchell%2C%20the%20national%20deputy%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Council%20on%20American-Islamic%20Relations%20(CAIR)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnation%2F2024%2F07%2F12%2Fdelta-palestine-flag-pin-apology%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20The%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20comment%20could%20make%20people%20think%20that%20the%20Palestinian%20flag%20is%20%26quot%3Ban%20icon%20of%20a%20hate%20group.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20happened%20with%20Delta%20is%20just%20the%20latest%20example%20of%20anti-Palestinian%20racism%2C%26quot%3B%20Mitchell%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20my%20hope%20is%20that%20this%20incident%20will%20begin%20to%20slowly%2C%20slowly%20move%20the%20needle%20in%20a%20different%20direction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAzka%20Mahmood%2C%20an%20executive%20director%20from%20the%20CAIR%20chapter%20in%20Georgia%2C%20said%20that%20equating%20the%20Palestinian%20flag%20with%20Hamas%20%26quot%3Berases%20the%20existence%20and%20legitimacy%20of%20the%20entirety%20of%20Palestine%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F07%2F12%2Fus%2Fdelta-employee-social-post-palestinian-reaj%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Palestinian%20flag%20represents%20a%20country%20and%20national%20aspirations%20of%20over%207%20million%20Palestinians%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20clear%20that%20some%20groups%20want%20to%20delegitimize%20the%20flag%20of%20Palestine%20entirely%2C%20suppress%20any%20expression%20of%20the%20existence%20of%20Palestine%2C%20and%20discourage%20open%20support%20for%20Palestinian%20rights.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CAIR%20said%20on%20X%20that%20it%20welcomed%20the%20apology%20from%20Delta%20and%20hoped%20that%20%26quot%3Bit%20sends%20a%20message%20to%20those%20who%20continue%20to%20dehumanize%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20as%20they%20face%20genocide%2C%20ethnic%20cleansing%20and%20forced%20starvation%20imposed%20by%20the%20far-right%20Israeli%20government%2C%20and%20enabled%20by%20the%20Biden%20admin.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.