n%20the%20state%20to%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections%2C%20three%20Independents%20-%20Hoshiyar%20Singh%20(Dehra)%2C%20Ashish%20Sharma%20(Hamirpur).%20and%20KL%20Thakur%20(Nalagarh)%20-%20were%20elected%20but%20they%20resigned%20after%20voting%20for%20BJP%20candidate%20Harsh%20Mahajan%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20election%20on%20February%2027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Independent%20MLAs%20resigned%20on%20March%2022%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP%20the%20next%20day.%20Their%20resignation%20was%20accepted%20by%20Speaker%20Kuldeep%20Singh%20Pathania%20on%20June%203%20and%20by-elections%20were%20held%20on%20July%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20former%20Independent%20legislators%20got%20tickets%20from%20the%20BJP%20but%20lost%20to%20Congress%20in%20two%20seats%20while%20the%20BJP%20won%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20election%20campaign%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Sukhu%20maintained%20that%20the%20Independent%20MLAs%20did%20not%20need%20to%20resign%20as%20%26quot%3Bthey%20can%20support%20or%20oppose%20any%20party%26quot%3B%20and%20questioned%20why%20they%20sought%20re-election%20after%2015%20months%20when%20they%20did%20not%20have%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Independent%20MLAs%20have%20played%20an%20important%20role%20in%20the%20state's%20electoral%20politics.%20Sixteen%20Independents%20were%20elected%20in%201967%20while%2012%20were%20elected%20in%201957%2C%20eight%20in%201952%2C%20seven%20each%20in%201972%20and%201993%2C%20six%20each%20in%201977%2C%201982%2C%20and%202003%2C%20five%20in%202012%2C%20three%20each%20in%201962%2C%202007%2C%20and%202022%2C%20two%20each%20in%201985%20and%202017%2C%20and%20one%20each%20in%201990%20and%201998.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201998%2C%20Romesh%20Dhawala%20who%20was%20the%20lone%20Independent%20MLA%2C%20emerged%20kingmaker%20as%20the%20Congress%20with%20his%20support%2C%20and%20BJP-HVC%20(Himachal%20Vikas%20Congress)%20combine%20had%2032%20members%20each%20in%20the%20House%20which%20had%20an%20effective%20strength%20of%2064.%20Elections%20in%20three%20snowbound%20tribal%20constituencies%20were%20slated%20for%20June%20while%20in%20another%20seat%20BJP%20MLA%20Varinder%20Kumar%20died%20before%20taking%20oath%2C%20necessitating%20a%20by-election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20single-largest%20party%2C%20Governor%20VS%20Ramadevi%20invited%20Congress%20leader%20Virbhadra%20Singh%20to%20form%20the%20government%20on%20March%206%2C%201998%2C%20and%20Mr%20Dhawala%20was%20inducted%20as%20a%20cabinet%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Virbhadra%20Singh%20announced%20his%20resignation%20in%20the%20House%20on%20March%2012%20without%20facing%20the%20floor%20test%2C%20and%20the%20assembly%20was%20held%20in%20suspended%20animation%20by%20the%20Governor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20Mr%20Dhawala%20extended%20support%20to%20the%20BJP-HVC%20combine%20and%20the%20Governor%20asked%20the%20BJP%20to%20form%20the%20government%20Prem%20Kumar%20Dhumal%20took%20oath%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20on%20March%2024%2C%20and%20Mr%20Dhawala%20was%20inducted%20as%20a%20minister%20in%20his%20cabinet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20that%20year%2C%20BJP-HVC%20won%20all%20four%20seats%20in%20the%20bypolls%20and%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20rose%20to%2036%20and%20the%20government%20lasted%20the%20full%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20year's%20Rajya%20Sabha%20election%20too%2C%20after%20both%20candidates%20got%2034%20votes%20each%2C%20the%20support%20of%20three%20Independents%20broke%20the%20deadlock%20and%20helped%20the%20BJP%20candidate%20win%20by%20a%20draw%20of%20lots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720889280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F9udqle78_kamlesh-thakur-ani_625x300_13_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22ori