-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%3A%20With%20Road%20Flooded%2C%20Medical%20College%20Principal%20Taken%20Out%20On%20A%20Stretcher%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20medical%20college%20principal%2C%20dressed%20in%20a%20shirt%20and%20trousers%2C%20is%20sitting%20on%20a%20stretcher%20as%20four%20men%20push%20it%20through%20a%20flooded%20street%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20showed%20a%20video.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20was%20reported%20from%20Shahjahanpur%2C%20which%20has%20received%20heavy%20rain%20and%20areas%20in%20the%20city%20are%20heavily%20flooded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20college%20principal%2C%20Rajesh%20Kumar%2C%20covering%20his%20face%20with%20a%20handkerchief%2C%20did%20not%20want%20to%20sully%20his%20clothes%20and%20got%20four%20men%20to%20take%20him%20out%20on%20a%20stretcher%2C%20say%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20principal%20has%20condemned%20the%20video%2C%20saying%20the%20reality%20is%20at%20variance%20with%20the%20video%20version.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20video%20is%20going%20viral%20which%20shows%20me%20being%20taken%20out%20on%20a%20stretcher.%20I%20condemn%20this%20video.%20Shahjahanpur%20is%20flooded.%20Even%20our%20college%20is%20flooded.%20Around%20300%20patients%2C%20working%20staff%20members%20and%20others%20are%20stuck%20here.%20We%20evacuated%20all%20the%20patients%2C%20using%20ambulance%2C%20buses%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWater%20has%20risen%20alarmingly.%20I%20tried%20if%20I%20could%20get%20an%20ambulance%20to%20get%20out.%20I%20have%20a%20leg%20injury%20and%20am%20also%20diabetic%2C%20due%20to%20which%20I%20am%20unable%20to%20walk.%20I%20spoke%20to%20my%20working%20staff%20members%20and%20they%20said%20they%20will%20take%20me%20out%20of%20the%20medical%20college%20on%20a%20stretcher%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Acharya%2C%20defending%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraffic%20on%20the%20Lucknow-Bareilly%20highw