t%20in%20an%20emphatic%20manner%20as%20he%20was%20glowing%20in%20his%20praise%20for%20young%20team%20comprising%20of%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20bunch%20of%20players%26quot%3B.%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20(93%20off%2053%20balls)%20and%20skipper%20Gill%20(58%20off%2039%20balls)%20hunted%20down%20a%20target%20of%20153%20with%2028%20balls%20to%20spare%20and%20the%20skipper%20expects%20this%20team%20to%20move%20forward%20in%20right%20direction.%20%26quot%3BChasing%20was%20one%20thing%20we%20talked%20about.%20We%20could%20not%20do%20it%20in%20the%20first%20game%2C%20so%20good%20to%20get%20it%20done.%20The%20job%20is%20not%20done%2C%20though%2C%26quot%3B%20Gill%20stated%20during%20the%20post-match%20presentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20great%20team%2C%20great%20bunch%20of%20players.%20Hopefully%2C%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20take%20the%20team%20forward.%26quot%3B%20With%20the%20series%20already%20in%20the%20pocket%2C%20when%20asked%20about%20changes%20in%20the%20playing%20XI%20for%20the%20final%20fixture%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Gill%20did%20not%20reveal%20anything%20significant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaven't%20had%20the%20discussion%20with%20the%20coach.%20If%20there%20are%20any%20changes%2C%20we%20will%20let%20you%20know%20at%20the%20toss%20tomorrow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Jaiswal%20was%20adjudged%20the%20man%20of%20the%20match%20for%20his%20commanding%20outing%20with%20the%20bat%2C%20while%20he%20admitted%20that%20he%20had%20to%20enjoy%20the%20decent%20batting%20turf%20at%20play%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20enjoyed%20my%20batting%20today.%20I%20had%20my%20plans%20for%20different%20bowlers.%20The%20ball%20was%20coming%20on%20when%20it%20was%20new%20and%20as%20it%20got%20old%2C%20it%20was%20quite%20slow.%20I%20enjoyed%20batting%20with%20Shubman%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20understood%20and%20changed%20my%20game.%20We%20really%20enjoyed%20together.%20Initially%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20go%20after%20my%20shots.%20After%20that%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20rotate%20and%20wanted%20to%20stay%20till%20the%20end.%26quot%3B%20Jaiswal%20said%20that%20for%20him%2C%20the%20more%20important%20aspect%20is%20his%20process%20of%20preparation.%20%26quot%3BMy%20diet%2C%20sleeping%20pattern%2C%20how%20I%20am%20executing%20my%20plans%20in%20practice%20However%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Zimbabwean%20captain%20Sikandar%20Raza%20had%20a%20contrasting%20take%20on%20the%20Harare%20pitch%2C%20which%20he%20felt%20was%20slow%2C%20especially%20when%20his%20team%20was%20put%20in%20to%20bat%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20because%20the%20wicket%20was%20a%20touch%20on%20the%20slower%20side%2C%20we%20thought%20160%20was%20a%20par%20score%2C%20but%20180%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20enough.%20Today%20is%20the%20day%20you%20hold%20your%20heads%20high%20and%20say%20they%20batted%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20opinionated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20heavy%20roller%20did%20the%20trick%20for%20them.%20It%20became%20a%20beautiful%20wicket.%26quot%3B%20But%20Raza%20expressed%20his%20confidence%20in%20the%20team%20gaining%20confidence%20and%20that%20they%20would%20become%20a%20competitive%20side%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20very%20sure%20we%20will%20be%20a%20very%20competitive%20side%20in%20a%20short%20time.%20There%20was%20a%20bit%20of%20kick%20(and)%20bounce%2C%20and%20we%20had%20to%20reign%20ourselves%20in.%20We%20will%20want%20to%20finish%20the%20series%203-2%20tomorrow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorked%20a%20lot%20on%20my%20cutters%20and%20yorkers%3A%20Khaleel%20Ahmed%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Khaleel%20bowled%20quite%20a%20few%20slower%20deliveries%2C%20and%20the%20trick%20worked%20against%20the%20Chevrons%2C%20as%20he%20seized%20the%20wickets%20of%20Dion%20Myers%20(12)%20and%20Clive%20Madande%20(7)%20in%20the%20closing%20stages%20of%20the%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20the%20same%2C%20the%2026-year-old%20thanked%20his%20stint%20as%20a%20reserve%20player%20for%20the%20Men%20in%20Blue%20during%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20the%20Americas%2C%20where%20he%20worked%20on%20his%20slower%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20part%20of%20the%20World%20Cup%20reserves%2C%20and%20there%2C%20I%20worked%20a%20lot%20on%20my%20cutters%20and%20yorkers.%20I%20am%20very%20happy%20with%20my%20performance.%20The%20kind%20of%20rhythm%20I%20have%20got%2C%20and%20the%20execution%20has%20been%20great%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20broadcaster%20following%20the%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20series%20is%20everything%20for%20me.%20When%20I%20was%20not%20part%20of%20the%20dressing%20room%2C%20I%20was%20missing%20it%20a%20lot.%20Very%20happy%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20it.%20We%20have%20all%20played%20in%20the%20IPL%3B%20we%20are%20all%20together%20in%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720887780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F6og0pjk8_yashasvi-jaiswal-shubman-gill-x-zimcricketv_625x300_13_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fzimbabwe-vs-india-2024%2Fnot-yashasvi-jaiswal-or-shubman-gill-sikandar-raza-opines-this-move-helped-india-beat-zimbabwe-by-10-wickets-6098992%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20(93%20off%2053%20balls)%20and%20skipper%20Gill%20(58%20off%2039%20balls)%20hunted%20down%20a%20target%20of%20153%20with%2028%20balls%20to%20spare%20vs%20Zimbabwe%20in%20fourth%20T20I.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fzimbabwe-vs-india-2024%2Fnot-yashasvi-jaiswal-or-shubman-gill-sikandar-raza-opines-this-move-helped-india-beat-zimbabwe-by-10-wickets-6098992%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22htt