ove-guru-teaches-women-how-marry-rich-makes-us19-million-year%3Fmodule%3Dtop_story%26pgtype%3Dsection%5C%22%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20influencer%20whose%20real%20name%20is%20Le%20Chuanqu%2C%C2%A0gained%20popularity%20in%20China%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Blove%20guru%26quot%3B%20by%20providing%20relationship%20and%20financial%20advice%20through%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%20earning%20a%20substantial%20following%20due%20to%20her%20unconventional%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-qa%3D%5C%22ContentHeadline-Container%5C%22%3EHowever%2C%20Qu%20Qu's%20advice%20often%20sparked%20controversy%2C%20as%20she%20encouraged%20behaviours%20that%20many%20considered%20to%20be%20unethical%20or%20manipulative%20in%20romantic%20relationships.%20Notably%2C%20she%20views%20relationships%20and%20marriage%20as%20a%20means%20of%20achieving%20financial%20gain%20and%20teaches%20women%20to%20do%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20refers%20to%20being%20married%20as%20''inside%20the%20fortress''%2C%20money%20as%20''rice''%2C%20and%20pregnancy%20as%20''carrying%20a%20ball''.%20In%20her%20videos%2C%20she%20bluntly%20stated%2C%20''All%20relationships%20are%20essentially%20about%20benefit%20exchanges.%20Everything%20should%20be%20used%20to%20boost%20my%20advantage%20and%20empower%20me.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20one-on-one%20consultation%20during%20her%20live-streams%20costs%20%24155%20(Rs%2012%2C945)%20while%20her%20most%20popular%20course%2C%20%26quot%3BValuable%20Relationships%26quot%3B%2C%20costs%20%24517%20(Rs%2043%2C179).%20Meanwhile%2C%20private%20counselling%20packages%20cost%20more%20than%20%241%2C400%20(Rs%C2%A01%2C16%2C927)%20per%20month.%20Beyond%20social%20media%2C%20Qu%20Qu%20also%20held%20workshops%20and%20seminars%20where%20she%20offered%20in-depth%20guidance%20on%20dating%20strategies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-qa%3D%5C%22ContentHeadline-Container%5C%22%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20she%20was%20banned%20from%20Weibo%20for%20promoting%20unhealthy%20relationship%20views%20and%20incorrect%20values.%20However%2C%20she%20now%20continues%20to%20use%20AI%20techniques%20to%20promote%20her%20business%20and%20direct%20customers%20to%20private%20channels.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-qa%3D%5C%22ContentHeadline-Container%5C%22%3EPublic%20opinion%20on%20her%20is%20divided%2C%20with%20some%20finding%20her%20approach%20to%20relationships%20to%20be%20realistic%20and%20empowering%2C%20while%20others%20find%20her%20to%20be%20hypocritical%20and%20teaching%20women%20to%20objectify%20themselves%20and%20use%20men%20for%20financial%20gain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-qa%3D%5C%22ContentHeadline-Container%5C%22%3EOne%20user%20wrote%2C%20''Her%20approach%20is%20understandable.%20What's%20wrong%20with%20wanting%20both%20love%20and%20money%3F%20This%20is%20a%20realistic%20society.%20Why%20shouldn't%20people%20strive%20for%20better%3F''%20Another%20commented%2C%20''She%20has%20profoundly%20impacted%20me%20this%20year.%20I've%20learned%20fundamental%20concepts%20like%20goal%20orientation%20and%20leveraging%20everything%20to%20empower%20myself.%20Her%20insights%20into%20recognising%20a%20man's%20true%20nature%20are%20invaluable.%20I%20highly%20recommend%20her.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-qa%3D%5C%22ContentHeadline-Container%5C%22%3EA%20third%20said%2C%20''She%20teaches%20girls%20to%20use%20men%20as%20cash%20cows%20and%20encourages%20competition%20among%20women.%20But%20she%20earns%20her%20living%20by%20working%20hard%20and%20relying%20on%20her%20efforts.%20Isn't%20that%20hypocritical%3F''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-qa%3D%5C%22ContentHeadline-Container%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720885620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fitg2tb78_dating_625x300_13_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fchinese-influencer-teaches-women-how-to-marry-rich-earns-rs-163-crore-per-year-6098847%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Qu%20Qu's%20advice%20often%20sparked%20controversy%2C%20as%20she%20en