0budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekebabs%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20ready%2C%20Raza%20suddenly%20has%20an%20idea.%20He%20looks%20around%20for%20a%20spare%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Indian%20flatbread)%20and%20puts%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekebabs%20%3C%2Fem%3Einto%20it%2C%20serving%20the%20%3Cem%3Esahib%3C%2Fem%3E%20his%20much-awaited%20snack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistory%20calls%20this%20moment%20the%20one%20where%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekathi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eroll%20was%20born!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FaJyz8f9XQSo%3Fsi%3DUfZb2ArDb5KspyWv%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInnovation%20at%20its%20best%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fleeting%20inclusion%20(of%20wrapping%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekebab%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20a%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3E)%20was%20an%20ingenious%20one%2C%20and%20soon%2C%20it%20became%20a%20norm%20at%20Nizam%E2%80%99s.%20Raza%20was%20quick%20to%20note%20how%20the%20idea%20put%20a%20smile%20on%20the%20%3Cem%3Esahib%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20face.%20From%20then%20on%2C%20Nizam%E2%80%99s%20decided%20to%20serve%20%E2%80%98that%20dish%E2%80%99%20to%20everyone%20who%20came%20to%20eat%20%3Cem%3Ekebabs%20%3C%2Fem%3Eat%20the%20restaurant.%20The%20fact%20that%20it%20became%20a%20no-mess%20affair%20for%20anyone%20who%20wanted%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F340611%2Fhealthy-snack-brand-startup-open-secret-woman-entrepreneur-ahana-gautam-iit-bombay-harvard%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrab%20a%20quick%20snack%3C%2Fa%3E%20ensured%20its%20longevity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20now%20for%20the%20story%20of%20the%20dish%E2%80%99s%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20hack%20of%20wrapping%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekebab%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20a%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Nizam%E2%80%99s%20also%20decided%20to%20tweak%20its%20strategy%20a%20little.%20The%20iron%20skewers%20that%20were%20in%20use%20were%20proving%20heavy%20and%20tedious%2C%20and%20so%2C%20these%20were%20swapped%20with%20substitutes%20made%20out%20of%20bamboo%20also%20called%20%3Cem%3Ekathi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(the%20Bengali%20word%20for%20stick).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fkathi-roll-1720596960.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kathi%20roll%20is%20a%20popular%20snack%20eaten%20around%20India%20and%20it%20comes%20in%20many%20varieties%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fkathi-roll-1720596960.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fkathi-roll-1720596960-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fkathi-roll-1720596960-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fkathi-roll-1720596960-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fkathi-roll-1720596960-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356192%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20kathi%20roll%20is%20a%20popular%20snack%20eaten%20around%20India%20and%20it%20comes%20in%20many%20varieties%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fid%3D106116087683016%26story_fbid%3D166139605013997%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKolkata%20Kathi%20Roll%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20time%2C%20the%20dish%20made%20it%20to%20the%20menu%20under%20the%20name%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ekathi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eroll%E2%80%99.%20And%20history%20smiled%20as%20it%20knew%20a%20cult%20favourite%20was%20born.%20In%20the%20years%20to%20come%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekathi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eroll%E2%80%99s%20definition%20expanded%20to%20include%20not%20just%20mutton%20%3Cem%3Ekebabs%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebut%20vegetarian%20options%20and%20egg-layered%20meats%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20snack%20that%20was%20invented%20as%20a%20hasty%20binge-eat%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekathi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eroll%20became%20etched%20in%20people%E2%80%99s%20memories%20for%20cultural%20reasons.%20As%20an%20article%20in%20%3Cem%3EMoney%20Control%3C%2Fem%3E%20underscores%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20roll%20during%20Durga%20Puja%2C%20it%20explores%20how%20amidst%20the%20slew%20of%20vendors%20selling%20fish%20fry%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekabiraji%3C%2Fem%3E%20(fried%20fish%20fillets)%2C%20chilli%20chicken%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F297834%2Fkolkata-phuchkawala-started-by-siblings-jyotirmoyee-debjyoti-saha-now-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ephuchkas%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20(fried%20%3Cem%3Epuris%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20are%20filled%20with%20mashed%20potatoes%2C%20tamarind%20pulp%2C%20black%20chickpeas%20and%20flavoured%20with%20red%20chilli%2C%20cumin%20powder%2C%20black%20salt)%2C%20there%20is%20bound%20to%20be%20a%20place%20selling%20%3Cem%3Ekathi%3C%2Fem%3E%20rolls%20with%20egg%20rolls%20being%20a%20crowd%20puller.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20side%20of%20nostalgia%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20Raj%20may%20have%20ended%20but%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekathi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eroll%20remained%20a%20permanent%20fixture%20on%20people%E2%80%99s%20minds%20and%20plates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F290130%2Forigin-of-samosa-sambhar-chaat-history-indian-food-recipes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efond%20memories%20of%20the%20snack%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20television%20journalist%2C%20food%20critic%2C%20and%20author%20of%20%E2%80%98The%20Indian%20Pantry%E2%80%99%20(2018)%2C%20Vir%20Sanghvi%20writes%20in%20a%20blog%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20many%20memories%20of%20eating%20at%20the%20original%20Nizam%E2%80%99s.%20A%20large%20%3Cem%3Etawa%20%3C%2Fem%3E(pan)%20which%20I%20was%20assured%20was%20a%20hundred%20years%20old%20(the%20next%20time%20I%20went%2C%20they%20said%2060%20years%20old%2C%20so%20let%E2%80%99s%20just%20agree%20it%20was%20very%20old)%20was%20put%20on%20an%20open%20fire.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20cook%20had%20already%20rolled%20a%20%3Cem%3Emaida%20paratha%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Indian%20flatbread%20made%20of%20refined%20flour)%20on%20the%20%3Cem%3Etawa%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Then%2C%20he%20broke%20an%20egg%20on%20the%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20cooked%20it%20on%20both%20sides%20so%20that%20the%20result%20was%20part%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20part%20omelette.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20goes%20on%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%20never%20forget%20those%20days%20in%201986%20when%20I%20would%20eat%20a%20Nizam%E2%80%99s%20roll%20for%20lunch%20every%20day.%20I%20had%20just%20come%20from%20Bombay%2C%20had%20no%20experience%20of%20rolls%20(a%20Frankie%20does%20not%20count%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20afraid%2C%20despite%20the%20resemblances)%20and%20was%20blown%20away%20by%20the%20excellence%20of%20the%20Nizam%E2%80%99s%20version.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FScreenshot-2024-07-10-131228_11zon-1720597507-500x496.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kathi%20rolls%20are%20versatile%20snacks%20and%20even%20extend%20to%20include%20fillings%20such%20as%20fish%2C%20paneer%20and%20eg