0the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rahul%20Bhushan%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20he%20runs%20a%20collective%20that%20hosts%20artists%E2%80%99%20residencies%20and%20acts%20as%20a%20regional%20centre%20that%20documents%20the%20architecture%2C%20way%20of%20life%2C%20regional%20culture%20and%20crafts%20of%20the%20region.%20The%20campus%20also%20doubles%20as%20a%20homestay%20which%20not%20only%20offers%20a%20peek%20into%20the%20beauty%20of%20the%20place%20but%20also%20the%20slow%20life%20of%20the%20area.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20really%20wanted%20to%20have%20a%20holistic%20view%20of%20things%20and%20promote%20our%20culture%20and%20vernacular%20architecture%20while%20hosting%20people%20in%20our%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F355205%2Fkerala-mud-homestay-mustafa-pa-converts-barren-mining-land-into-forest-greenara%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esustainable%20homestay%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20are%20sharing%20a%20way%20of%20life%20here%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENestled%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Naggar%2C%20amid%20the%20Deodar%20trees%2C%20the%20views%20that%20the%20homestay%20offers%20is%20like%20a%20dream%20come%20true.%20A%20visual%20delight%2C%20the%20place%20overlooks%20the%20Beas%20River%20and%20the%20majestic%20Dhauladhar%20range.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20magnificent%20homestay%20overlooking%20these%20views%20started%20as%20a%20collective%20to%20save%20the%20heritage%2C%20culture%20and%20vernacular%20architecture%20of%20the%20area.%20So%20what%20led%20to%20the%20foundation%20of%20this%20homestay%3F%20Rahul%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20my%20masters%20in%20architecture%2C%20I%20focused%20my%20research%20thesis%20on%20indigenous%20building%20practices%20in%20the%20western%20