%2C%20we%20instead%20store%20the%20excess%20energy%20and%20use%20it%20during%20non-generation%20hours%2C%20say%20during%20the%20nights%20and%20cloudy%20days.%20We%20have%20our%20own%20backup.%20As%20long%20as%20I%20am%20dependent%20on%20the%20grid%2C%20we%20are%20responsible%20for%20coal-backed%20power%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20the%20major%20production%20of%20electricity%20is%20achieved%20through%20coal%20thermal%20power%20plants%20which%20is%20around%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coal.nic.in%2Fen%2Fmajor-statistics%2Fgeneration-of-thermal-power-from-raw-coal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E75%20percent%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20the%20total%20power%20generation.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20want%20to%20reduce%20your%20carbon%20footprint%2C%20you%20need%20to%20reduce%20your%20dependence%20on%20coal%20and%20thermal%20energy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBesides%2C%20if%20the%20grid%20in%20the%20net-metre%20system%20decides%20to%20shut%20down%2C%20my%20house%20will%20still%20be%20in%20darkness%20even%20though%20I%20am%20generating%20power%20from%20solar%20energy.%20The%20grid-backed%20system%20helps%20us%20create%20power%20backup%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESelf-dependent%20on%20energy%20%26amp%3B%20water%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20couple%20has%20not%20given%20up%20on%20their%20electricity%20metre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-1_11zon-1720701302.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20planned%20a%20grid%20backed%20solar%20photovoltaic%20(PV)%20system%20in%20the%20house%20with%20a%2015%20kWp%20capacity.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-1_11zon-1720701302.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-1_11zon-1720701302-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-1_11zon-1720701302-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-1_11zon-1720701302-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-1_11zon-1720701302-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356501%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20couple%20planned%20a%20grid%20backed%20solar%20photovoltaic%20(PV)%20system%20in%20the%20house%20with%20a%2015%20kWp%20capacity.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20only%20I%20was%20convinced%20about%20this%20setup%2C%20so%20we%20had%20to%20keep%20the%20grid%20as%20a%20backup.%20We%20have%20programmed%20the%20system%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20firstly%20it%20consumes%20the%20solar%20power%2C%20then%20it%20takes%20power%20from%20batteries%20during%20non-generation%20hours.%20If%20the%20battery%20ever%20drops%2C%20it%E2%80%99ll%20take%20power%20from%20the%20grid%2C%20which%20hardly%20happens.%20The%20entire%20system%20works%20seamlessly%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Suneet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20nearly%2010%20months%20a%20year%2C%20the%20couple%20claims%20to%20use%20zero%20energy%20from%20the%20grid.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20consume%20some%20energy%20from%20the%20grid%20for%20about%20two%20months%20in%20the%20summer%20when%20we%20have%20to%20run%20the%20air%20conditioner%20by%20the%20night.%20Sometimes%2C%20there%20isn%E2%80%99t%20enough%20generation%20in%20the%20day%20to%20run%20the%20AC%20at%20all%20hours%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20we%20end%20up%20having%20Rs%201%2C500-Rs%202%2C000%20bills%20in%20those%20months%2C%20of%20which%20the%20fixed%20metre%20charge%20is%20about%20Rs%20500%20to%20700%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20setup%20cost%20the%20couple%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20and%20they%20believe%20they%20would%20get%20the%20return%20on%20investment%20within%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20limitations%20of%20the%20entire%20grid-backed%20setup%2C%20Shilpa%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COver%20the%20years%2C%20we%20developed%20a%20habit%20of%20running%20the%20washing%20machine%2C%20the%20mixer%2C%20water%20pumps%20only%20in%20the%20solar%20hours%20between%2010am%20to%205pm%20or%20it%20will%20lead%20to%20storage%20exhaustion.%20We%20run%20four%20ACs%20in%20the%20day%20and%20only%20two%20at%20night.%20You%20require%20this%20kind%20of%20discipline.%20But%20these%20are%20all%20matters%20of%20choice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-2-1720701386.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20harness%20solar%20energy%20to%20use%20energy%20consuming%20appliances%20like%20induction%2C%20microwave%2C%20washing%20machine.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-2-1720701386.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-2-1720701386-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-2-1720701386-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-2-1720701386-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-2-1720701386-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356504%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20couple%20harness%20solar%20energy%20to%20use%