s%20expectations%20and%20gauge%20the%20adequacy%20of%20my%20preparation.%20Additionally%2C%20I%20focused%20on%20mastering%20subjects%20that%20typically%20challenge%20other%20candidates%2C%20giving%20me%20a%20competitive%20edge.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20gain%20an%20edge%20over%20his%20competitors%2C%20Harsimran%20stressed%20reverse%20engineering.%20%E2%80%9CI%20identified%20the%20most%20challenging%20questions%20from%20previous%20years%E2%80%99%20question%20papers%20and%20diligently%20searched%20for%20relevant%20information%20online.%20Once%20I%20found%20the%20appropriate%20source%20books%2C%20I%20stuck%20to%20them%20to%20gain%20a%20deeper%20understanding%20of%20the%20subjects%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20strategy%2C%20he%20successfully%20cleared%20the%20Prelims%20and%20Mains%20stages%20in%202022.%20He%20mentions%20that%20he%20dedicated%20approximately%20a%20month%20and%20a%20half%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20interview%20round.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20interview%20rounds%20for%20both%20CSE%20and%20IFS%20are%20different.%20While%20the%20former%20is%20on%20general%20questions%2C%20the%20latter%20stresses%20on%20technicalities%20of%20the%20forest%20service%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20general%20answers%20might%20suffice%20in%20the%20Civil%20Services%20Examination%20(CSE)%2C%20the%20board%20for%20the%20Indian%20Forest%20Service%20(IFS)%20expects%20scientific%20and%20sustainable%20solutions%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Harsimran%2C%20who%20secured%20210%20marks%20out%20of%20300%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F347452%2Fupsc-cse-samyak-jain-visually-impaired-assistant-collector-puducherry-topper-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epersonality%20test%20round%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20preparing%20for%20the%20interview%2C%20I%20covered%20basic%20questions%20about%20my%20backgr